items.name: Sabrent 4-Port USB 2.0 Hub with Power Switches
items.shortDescription: Add up to four peripherals quickly and easily with the Sabrent 4-Port USB 2.0 Hub. It's a good choice for expanding any computer, and it's especially suitable for notebooks which come with only a few ports. Use this item when you need to attach many USB devices at once, such as a printer, card reader, cell phone, Apple iPod, thumb drive, mouse, keyboard or an external hard drive. Power switches on this Sabrent USB hub allow for easy on/off operation. An LED light tells you when it's functioning. Achieve a full 480 Mbps on each port, or daisy-chain multiple hubs to a maximum of 127 devices. The streamlined design pairs well with other electronics and accessories to help your area stay looking tidy and organized. Its compact size makes it easy to transport along with a notebook, tablet or other device. The Sabrent 4-Port USB 2.0 Hub is fully backwards compatible with USB 1.1 products.
